The Name Blessed Irene Stefani, Or Nyaadtha, Commands Admiration And Respect From Many Catholic Faithfuls Worldwide, Owing To Her Selfless Actions For The People Of Mukurweyni Back In The 1920s. And Those Who Got To Interact With The Catholic Sister Considered Themselves Lucky. One Such Person Is Mama Emma Wangechi From Nyeri County, Who As A Child Was Taught By Nyaadtha.